import bpy

def shader_material(material: bpy.types.Material):
    material.use_nodes = True
    nodes = material.node_tree.nodes
    links = material.node_tree.links

    # Create nodes
    material_output = nodes.new('ShaderNodeOutputMaterial')
    mix_shader = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMixShader')
    colorramp = nodes.new('ShaderNodeValToRGB')
    noise_texture = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexNoise')
    texture_coordinate = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexCoord')
    principled_bsdf = nodes.new('ShaderNodeBsdfPrincipled')
    bump = nodes.new('ShaderNodeBump')
    light_path = nodes.new('ShaderNodeLightPath')

    # Create links to connect nodes
    links.new(mix_shader.outputs[0], material_output.inputs[0])
    links.new(colorramp.outputs[0], mix_shader.inputs[0])
    links.new(principled_bsdf.outputs[0], mix_shader.inputs[1])
    links.new(light_path.outputs[0], mix_shader.inputs[2])
    links.new(noise_texture.outputs[0], colorramp.inputs[0])
    links.new(texture_coordinate.outputs[3], noise_texture.inputs[0])
    links.new(bump.outputs[0], principled_bsdf.inputs[22])
    links.new(noise_texture.outputs[0], bump.inputs[2])

    # Set parameters for each node
    colorramp.color_ramp.elements[1].position = 0.5
    colorramp.color_ramp.elements.new(1.0)
    colorramp.color_ramp.elements[2].color = [0.5, 0.0, 0.5, 1.0]
    noise_texture.inputs[2].default_value = 2.0
    noise_texture.inputs[3].default_value = 10.0
    noise_texture.inputs[4].default_value = 1.0
    noise_texture.inputs[5].default_value = 0.1
    principled_bsdf.inputs[0].default_value = [0.2, 0.5, 0.8, 1.0]
    principled_bsdf.inputs[6].default_value = 0.4
    principled_bsdf.inputs[7].default_value = 0.2
    bump.inputs[1].default_value = 0.1

    material.use_nodes = True
    nodes = material.node_tree.nodes
    links = material.node_tree.links

    # Create nodes
    material_output = nodes.new('ShaderNodeOutputMaterial')
    principled_bsdf = nodes.new('ShaderNodeBsdfPrincipled')
    mix = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMixRGB')
    voronoi_texture = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexVoronoi')
    mapping = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMapping')
    musgrave_texture = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexMusgrave')
    texture_coordinate = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexCoord')

    # Create links to connect nodes
    links.new(principled_bsdf.outputs[0], material_output.inputs[0])
    links.new(mix.outputs[0], principled_bsdf.inputs[0])
    links.new(voronoi_texture.outputs[1], mix.inputs[1])
    links.new(musgrave_texture.outputs[0], mix.inputs[2])
    links.new(mapping.outputs[0], voronoi_texture.inputs[0])
    links.new(texture_coordinate.outputs[2], musgrave_texture.inputs[0])

    # Set parameters for each node
    principled_bsdf.inputs[20].default_value = 1.2
    voronoi_texture.inputs[2].default_value = -5.0
    mapping.inputs[3].default_value = [2.0, 0.5, 0.5]
    musgrave_texture.inputs[2].default_value = 2.0
    musgrave_texture.inputs[3].default_value = 10.0

    nodes = material.node_tree.nodes
    links = material.node_tree.links

    # Create nodes
    material_output = nodes.new('ShaderNodeOutputMaterial')
    mix_shader = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMixShader')
    glossy_bsdf = nodes.new('ShaderNodeBsdfGlossy')
    principled_bsdf = nodes.new('ShaderNodeBsdfPrincipled')
    colorramp = nodes.new('ShaderNodeValToRGB')
    noise_texture = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexNoise')
    mapping = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMapping')
    texture_coordinate = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexCoord')
    multiply = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMath')
    wave_texture = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexWave')

    # Create links to connect nodes
    links.new(mix_shader.outputs[0], material_output.inputs[0])
    links.new(glossy_bsdf.outputs[0], mix_shader.inputs[1])
    links.new(principled_bsdf.outputs[0], mix_shader.inputs[2])
    links.new(colorramp.outputs[0], principled_bsdf.inputs[0])
    links.new(noise_texture.outputs[0], colorramp.inputs[0])
    links.new(mapping.outputs[0], noise_texture.inputs[0])
    links.new(multiply.outputs[0], noise_texture.inputs[1])
    links.new(texture_coordinate.outputs[3], mapping.inputs[0])
    links.new(wave_texture.outputs[1], multiply.inputs[0])
    links.new(wave_texture.outputs[1], multiply.inputs[1])

    # Set parameters for each node
    glossy_bsdf.inputs[0].default_value = [0.2, 0.2, 0.2, 1.0]
    principled_bsdf.inputs[20].default_value = 0.5
    colorramp.color_ramp.elements[0].color = [0.05, 0.0, 1.0, 1.0]
    colorramp.color_ramp.elements[1].position = 0.5
    colorramp.color_ramp.elements[1].color = [0.0, 1.0, 0.0, 1.0]
    colorramp.color_ramp.elements.new(0.75)
    colorramp.color_ramp.elements[2].color = [1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0]
    noise_texture.inputs[2].default_value = 2.0
    noise_texture.inputs[3].default_value = 5.0
    multiply.operation = 'MULTIPLY'
    wave_texture.inputs[2].default_value = 10.0
    wave_texture.inputs[6].default_value = 3.14

    nodes = material.node_tree.nodes
    links = material.node_tree.links

    # Create nodes
    material_output = nodes.new('ShaderNodeOutputMaterial')
    principled_bsdf = nodes.new('ShaderNodeBsdfPrincipled')
    mix = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMixRGB')
    add = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMath')
    voronoi_texture = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexVoronoi')
    noise_texture = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexNoise')
    texture_coordinate = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexCoord')
    bump = nodes.new('ShaderNodeBump')

    # Create links to connect nodes
    links.new(principled_bsdf.outputs[0], material_output.inputs[0])
    links.new(mix.outputs[0], principled_bsdf.inputs[0])
    links.new(bump.outputs[0], principled_bsdf.inputs[22])
    links.new(add.outputs[0], mix.inputs[1])
    links.new(voronoi_texture.outputs[0], mix.inputs[2])
    links.new(voronoi_texture.outputs[1], add.inputs[0])
    links.new(noise_texture.outputs[1], add.inputs[1])
    links.new(texture_coordinate.outputs[3], noise_texture.inputs[0])

    # Set parameters for each node
    principled_bsdf.inputs[6].default_value = 0.5
    mix.inputs[0].default_value = 0.3
    voronoi_texture.inputs[2].default_value = 3.0
    noise_texture.inputs[3].default_value = 10.0
    bump.inputs[0].default_value = 0.2

    material.use_nodes = True
    nodes = material.node_tree.nodes
    links = material.node_tree.links

    # Create nodes
    material_output = nodes.new('ShaderNodeOutputMaterial')
    principled_bsdf = nodes.new('ShaderNodeBsdfPrincipled')
    mix = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMixRGB')
    noise_texture = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexNoise')
    mapping = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMapping')
    texture_coordinate = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexCoord')
    mix_1 = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMixRGB')
    subtract = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMath')
    wave_texture = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexWave')
    bump = nodes.new('ShaderNodeBump')

    # Create links to connect nodes
    links.new(principled_bsdf.outputs[0], material_output.inputs[0])
    links.new(mix.outputs[0], principled_bsdf.inputs[0])
    links.new(mix_1.outputs[0], principled_bsdf.inputs[9])
    links.new(bump.outputs[0], principled_bsdf.inputs[22])
    links.new(noise_texture.outputs[0], mix.inputs[1])
    links.new(mapping.outputs[0], noise_texture.inputs[0])
    links.new(texture_coordinate.outputs[0], mapping.inputs[0])
    links.new(subtract.outputs[0], mix_1.inputs[0])
    links.new(wave_texture.outputs[0], subtract.inputs[0])
    links.new(noise_texture.outputs[1], subtract.inputs[1])

    # Set parameters for each node
    mix.inputs[2].default_value = [0.8, 0.2, 0.1, 1.0]
    noise_texture.inputs[1].default_value = 5.0
    mix_1.inputs[1].default_value = [0.2, 0.2, 0.2, 1.0]
    mix_1.inputs[2].default_value = [1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0]
    subtract.operation = 'SUBTRACT'

    wave_texture.inputs[4].default_value = 0.0

    mix_2 = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMixRGB')

    colorramp_2 = nodes.new('ShaderNodeValToRGB')
    add = nodes.new('ShaderNodeMath')
    musgrave_texture = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexMusgrave')
    texture_coordinate = nodes.new('ShaderNodeTexCoord')

    # Create links to connect nodes
    links.new(principled_bsdf.outputs[0], material_output.inputs[0])
    links.new(mix.outputs[0], principled_bsdf.inputs[0])
    links.new(noise_texture_2.outputs[0], principled_bsdf.inputs[6])

    links.new(colorramp_1.outputs[0], mix_2.inputs[2])

    links.new(noise_texture_1.outputs[0], mix_3.inputs[2])
